en_527337_0	Brigadier Lakshman Fernando assumed office as the new Commander, Forward Maintenance Area - North on Thursday (15).
en_527337_1	He placed his signature in an official document to mark the assumption of duties, amidst chanting of ‘Seth Pirith’ in the presence of Staff Officers.
en_527337_2	He planted a coconut sapling to mark the event and addressed the troops under command to the Forward Maintenance Area - North.
en_527337_3	Brigadier Lakshman Fernando, prior to this new appointment served as the Director of Administration, Teaching Hospital, Kotelawala Defence University.
